codex
The regression reproduces exactly: parsing succeeds, but `set_enabled` builds a new one-key dictionary, so every unknown top-level key—and therefore its nested content—is lost. The minimal fix is to mutate only `enabled` on the parsed object before serializing it with the existing formatting.
apply patch
patch: completed
